    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in an impeccable state, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, adheres strictly to original factory specifications. Mechanical integrity is absolute, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. We invite discerning enthusiasts to inspect this peerless example of engineering and care.",
