      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered every single day. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014seriously, it's absolutely flawless! I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out and come see it for yourself; I promise you're going to fall in love at first sight! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
