    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp gates, channeling power to a Variable M Differential Lock. The suspension remains tight, retaining factory-spec damping and bushing elasticity. Finished in its original paint with exceptional depth and zero panel gap variance, this M3 represents a turn-key acquisition for the collector prioritizing mechanical purity and atmospheric performance.",
